Lecture 3 (Gateways, Protocols and Cloud Platforms)

IoT not just as individual devices, but as an ecosystem of connected systems and infrastructures. 
Data communication and integration between layers are crucial to how IoT truly functions.

Workshop 3

Interaction design always needs to consider technical feasibility first, whether our materials (like Lego or paper) and skills can actually support the design.
Prototyping NEED TO make the balance between “feasibility” and “experience”.
